{"tid":1953280,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"被捕手足有野想講","createTime":"2020-04-01T05:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T06:02:35.000Z","uid":182907,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"61933c59a0f80212aec0cc9b31019e2869536d14","tid":1953280,"uid":182907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T05:51:13.000Z","msg":"近依兩三個月 連登既分化開始好嚴重<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鬥黃Post 鹹濕Post 假新聞 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n請大家好好咁去睇一下我哋係點樣行過頭嗰半年 <br />\n我地係點樣從和勇互屌 進化到和勇不割<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">焦點集中 不停進化 </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">互相包容 有錯就認</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我認識既一啲人/admin 已經不問世事<br />\n想問仲關心呢件事嘅你 可唔可以應承我唔好放棄<br />\n我嘅犧牲唔算多 但我見到身邊嘅人犧牲左好多好多<br />\n我知道更加唔可以係呢個時間放棄 <br />\n香港人 可唔可以陪我撐落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5becedabda9a74e65c31d9508d6652ab34a06da8","tid":1953280,"uid":182907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T05:52:34.000Z","msg":"輕輕推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d21d6591048baddf2d97596c9638533b4c41bf8","tid":1953280,"uid":182907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T05:53:20.000Z","msg":"用錯不推文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5bb3e5ba7230484762f26f2c52be1d25997bdf","tid":1953280,"uid":31022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T05:53:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1dc71d37a19461709466fec7c7f1b6d8f8cb0005","tid":1953280,"uid":182907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T05:54:04.000Z","msg":"大家可唔可以一齊掙扎"},{"pid":"d5788dead28ebf1434b68ec582a84bb7ae083306","tid":1953280,"uid":128287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco